OL,3,CX Factor star-turned-activist Rebecca
OL,4,CFerguson made MBE
OL,6,FBritish singer Rebecca Ferguson, who
OL,7,Ffirst found fame on The X Factor but
OL,8,Fhas since become an activist in the
OL,9,Fmusic industry, has been awarded an
OL,10,FMBE in the King's Birthday Honours.
OL,12,FThe Liverpool-born performer, who was
OL,13,Fa runner-up on the ITV series in 2010,
OL,14,Fis made a Member of the Order of the
OL,15,FBritish Empire for her services to the
OL,16,Fmusic industry.
