OL,3,CX Factor star-turned-activist Rebecca
OL,4,CFerguson made MBE
OL,6,FThe 37-year-old originally studied to
OL,7,Fbecome a legal secretary before making
OL,8,Fher name on the singing competition,
OL,9,Fbeating One Direction to second place
OL,10,Fwhile Matt Cardle was named champion.
OL,12,FFollowing her success on The X Factor,
OL,13,FFerguson went on to release several
OL,14,Falbums and became a panellist on ITV's
OL,15,FLoose Women.
OL,17,FHer debut album Heaven, released in
OL,18,F2011, peaked at number three on the UK
OL,19,Falbums chart.
