OL,3,CX Factor star-turned-activist Rebecca
OL,4,CFerguson made MBE
OL,6,FFerguson also featured on the Justice
OL,7,FCollective's star-studded remake of He
OL,8,FAin't Heavy, He's My Brother, which
OL,9,Ftriumphed as the UK's Christmas number
OL,10,Fone track in 2012.
OL,12,FThe singer later turned her hand to
OL,13,Factivism within the industry.
OL,15,FIn 2021, Ferguson met former culture
OL,16,Fsecretary Oliver Dowden to discuss
OL,17,Fdiscrimination in the music industry,
OL,18,Fa meeting which she described at the
OL,19,Ftime as "very productive".
