OL,3,CX Factor star-turned-activist Rebecca
OL,4,CFerguson made MBE
OL,6,FIt came as she campaigned for the
OL,7,Fintroduction of a regulatory body for
OL,8,Fthe sector, which would work to ensure
OL,9,Fartist welfare.
OL,11,FIn September last year, Ferguson gave
OL,12,Fevidence to MPs on the Women And
OL,13,FEqualities Committee as part of a 2023-
OL,14,F2024 report into misogyny and
OL,15,Fdiscrimination in the UK music
OL,16,Findustry.
