OL,4,CFerguson made MBE
OL,6,FFerguson criticised music managers and
OL,7,Fagents, whom she claimed manipulate
OL,8,Fartists, during the inquiry which
OL,9,Fexamined misogynistic attitudes that
OL,10,Fexist in the industry and what steps
OL,11,Fcould be taken to improve attitudes
OL,12,Fand treatment of women.
OL,14,FEarlier this year Ferguson said being
OL,15,Fvocal about her experience in the
OL,16,Fmusic industry has brought her "a lot
OL,17,Fof peace".
