OL,3,CX Factor star-turned-activist Rebecca
OL,4,CFerguson made MBE
OL,6,FFerguson also previously called on
OL,7,Fmedia watchdog Ofcom to conduct an
OL,8,Finvestigation into reality TV shows to
OL,9,F"ensure the future safety of
OL,10,Fcontestants."
OL,12,FOn X, formerly Twitter, she posted a
OL,13,Fscreenshot of an email which she said
OL,14,Fshe sent to ITV and Ofcom in 2021
OL,15,Fmaking a "formal complaint" in
OL,16,Frelation to the treatment of
OL,17,Fcontestants on reality shows but said
OL,18,F"my concerns appeared to be fobbed
OL,19,Foff".
