OL,3,CX Factor star-turned-activist Rebecca
OL,4,CFerguson made MBE
OL,6,FAt the time, a spokesperson for Ofcom
OL,7,Fsaid they "listened carefully to the
OL,8,Fextent of her concerns about the
OL,9,Ftreatment of contestants during her
OL,10,Ftime on The X Factor in 2010" when
OL,11,Fthey met her virtually in 2021.
OL,13,FA statement from ITV said the
OL,14,Fbroadcaster was "committed to having
OL,15,Fin place suitable processes to protect
OL,16,Fthe mental health and welfare of
OL,17,Fprogramme participants".
OL,19,FIn 2016, Ferguson revealed she had
OL,20,Fbeen abused in a children's home at
OL,21,Fthe age of eight.
